sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/JupyterHub
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as Notebook Controller
    participant Registry as Container Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant StatefulSet as StatefulSet
    participant NotebookPod as Notebook Pod<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant Culler as Culling Controller<br/>(Timer-based)
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    %% Flow 1: Notebook Creation
    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over User,StatefulSet: Flow 1: Notebook Creation
        User->>K8sAPI: Create Notebook CR<br/>Auth: User credentials
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch event<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create StatefulSet<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Service (ClusterIP)<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        alt USE_ISTIO=true
            Controller->>K8sAPI: Create VirtualService<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        end
        StatefulSet->>Registry: Pull notebook image<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ImagePullSecrets
        Registry-->>StatefulSet: Container image
        StatefulSet->>NotebookPod: Start pod
    end

    %% Flow 2: Idle Notebook Culling
    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
        Note over Culler,NotebookPod: Flow 2: Idle Notebook Culling (IDLENESS_CHECK_PERIOD=1m)
        loop Every IDLENESS_CHECK_PERIOD
            Culler->>NotebookPod: GET /notebook/{ns}/{name}/api/kernels<br/>8888/TCP HTTP plaintext<br/>Auth: None
            NotebookPod-->>Culler: Kernel activity status
            Culler->>NotebookPod: GET /notebook/{ns}/{name}/api/terminals<br/>8888/TCP HTTP plaintext<br/>Auth: None
            NotebookPod-->>Culler: Terminal activity status
            alt Idle > CULL_IDLE_TIME (default 1440m)
                Culler->>K8sAPI: Update Notebook CR<br/>Add kubeflow-resource-stopped annotation<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
                K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch event
                Controller->>K8sAPI: Scale StatefulSet to 0<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
            end
        end
    end

    %% Flow 3: Metrics Collection
    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Prometheus,Controller: Flow 3: Metrics Collection
        loop Every scrape interval
            Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP plaintext<br/>Auth: None
            Controller-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics<br/>notebook_running, notebook_create_total, etc.
        end
    end
